<Link id="l00160" /><CodeLine lineNumber="160"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//  where th can be omitted when it is 0 dcbtst is the same.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00161" /><CodeLine lineNumber="161"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// On AIX, only emit the extended mnemonics for dcbt and dcbtst if</span></CodeLine>
